messageBody:
Hello friends,
I am new to junit. I've downloaded 3.8.1. I didn't know how to start.
I have developed a project using java swing. It has 3 modules and 8 java programs.
I have to test my project (unit testing, integration testing).
Can anyone tell me a way to start testing and what are the procedures.
I can understand if you provide any example illustrations for a simple program.
Kindly provide if there is any tutorial link to start with JUnit.

Thanking you in Advance,
S.Muthuvel.
